To configure prv, do the following:

* Copy prv.json.default to prv.json
* Modify prv.json to your liking

Remove any parameters in prv.json for which you would like to use the defaults.

Note that prv.json.default is maintained in the git repo whereas prv.json is not.

If you are running the docker version, be sure to add:
-v $PWD/prv.json:/base/prv.json so your configuration is picked up at run time.